Hi @benbarsdell

Finally it worked. I ran the following command under "bazel-bin/inception/imagenet_train.runfiles/main/" directory where as it should on the current directory.

$ touch inception/__init__.py
$ touch inception/slim/__init__.py

Now I am able to get NV profile.

Thanks 👍

body:
Hi @benbarsdell 

Finally it worked. I ran the following command under "bazel-bin/inception/imagenet_train.runfiles/**main**/" directory where as it should on the current directory. 

```
$ touch inception/__init__.py
$ touch inception/slim/__init__.py
```

Now I am able to get NV profile.

Thanks :+1:
